javax.jcr

Class PropertyType

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.jcr.PropertyType

  •  
    public final class PropertyType
extends java.lang.Object
    The property types supported by the JCR standard.

    This interface defines following property types:

    • STRING
    • BINARY
    • LONG
    • DOUBLE
    • DATE
    • BOOLEAN
    • NAME
    • PATH
    • REFERENCE
